# Fergus' vim setup

## Installation

### Add Pathogen
cd ~/.vim/
mkdir autoload
cp ~/Projects/config/vim-pathogen/autoload/pathogen.vim autoload/

### Add plugins
cd ~/.vim/
mkdir bundle
git submodule add https://github.com/fergusb/vim-foo.git bundle/foo

### Init plugins
cd ~/.vim/
git submodule init
git submodule update

### Update plugins
git submodule foreach git pull origin master


" vim:ft=mkd
